<%- include('./partials/header') %>

<div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">A Comprehensive Platform for Modern Education</h1>
    <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
        <p class="lead mb-4">
            Our Student Management System provides a seamless, all-in-one solution for tracking attendance, managing academic marks, and generating insightful reports. Please use the navigation bar to log in and get started.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container px-4 py-5" id="features">
    <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom text-center mb-5">What Our System Offers</h2>

    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="feature-card-icon mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Role-Based Security</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        A secure authentication system with two distinct roles. Administrators have full control to manage all data, while Students can only view their personal dashboard, ensuring complete data privacy.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="feature-card-icon mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-calendar-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Automated Attendance Tracking</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Admins can efficiently mark daily attendance. The system automatically calculates percentages and generates a defaulters list for students with attendance below 75%, saving valuable time.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="feature-card-icon mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-pencil-square"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Centralized Marks System</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        A complete CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) system for managing marks across various exams. Data is organized and easily accessible for both admins and students.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="feature-card-icon mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-person-badge"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Personalized Student Dashboard</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Students can log in to view a private dashboard showing a clean summary of their attendance percentag per subject and a detailed breakdown of their academic marks.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

